(211, 1, '2018-01-09 08:09:32', '2018-01-09 08:09:32', 'The goal of the Pizza Harvest is to show that Pizzas come from farms and not factories.  This one acre living pizza exhibit is filled with all the ingredients needed for yummy pizza!\r\n<img src=\"http://webdev.wordpress-developer.us/mary-land-farm/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/1.jpg\" class=\"alignright\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<p class=\"highLightTxt\">\r\nWe are now scheduling field trips for the Spring of 2018.\r\n</p>', 'PIZZA HARVEST', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '22-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-01-09 08:09:32', '2018-01-09 08:09:32', '', 22, 'http://webdev.wordpress-developer.us/mary-land-farm/22-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
